This user interface displays data for one entry of the [[Tools table]].  Entities in it are: 

* Name: the name given to this tool
* Description: free-text description of the tool
* Tags: user-given tags for this tool
* Languages: free-text list of coding languages used in this tool
* Comments: a set of user comments about this tool

The tool gui design and table design have been reconciled with each other. 